&lt;p&gt;Loop through the JSON with a &lt;code&gt;foreach&lt;/code&gt; loop as key-value pairs. Do type-checking to determine if more looping needs to be done.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-php s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-php&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;foreach&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-variable&quot;&gt;$json_a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-variable&quot;&gt;$key&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-variable&quot;&gt;$value&lt;/span&gt;) {
    &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-variable&quot;&gt;$key&lt;/span&gt;;
